title: Kim Kardashian’s bizarre New York Fashion Week outfit | The
text:
KIM Kardashian has taken a completely different approach to her pregnancy wardrobe this time around, opting for block colours and long coats.
But the normally impeccably groomed reality TV star stunned New York’s fashion set with a bizarre nipple-teasing ensemble.
The 34-year-old, who is pregnant with her second child with Kanye West, stepped out on Saturday in an outfit that left onlookers scratching their heads.
Misstep ... Kim Kardashian stunned onlookers in New York with a bizarre Fashion Week ensemble. Picture: Splash News Source: Supplied
The mum-of-one sported a low-cut ripped top, a high-cut leather miniskirt, suede thigh-high boots and an oversized coat.
The brunette beauty has mostly worn tight, revealing dresses during her pregnancy, but this time opted for a much racier style.
Racy ... Kim Kardashian’s baby bump was on display. Picture: Splash News Source: Supplied
Little to the imagination ... Kim Kardashian debuted a new look at New York Fashion Week. Picture: Splash News Source: Supplied
The social media guru has been experimenting with her style while in the Big Apple for New York Fashion Week.
A couple of days ago, Kim stepped out in a ruffled peplum skirt and camel over-the-knee-boots she said were part of her husband’s new Yeezy collection.
Yeezy boots (Frame content direct link: https://instagram.com/p/7eWBwhOSyi/embed .)
On Friday, Mrs Kardashian West again flaunted her extreme cleavage in a black lace gown for Givenchy’s first-ever New York show at NYFW, where sister Kendall Jenner walked the runway.
Fashion couple (Frame content direct link: https://instagram.com/p/7irwFJOSzq/embed .)
What do you think of Kim Kardashian’s pregnancy style?
